an intent to launch a

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:19.230
music player like this.

00:10:19.230 --> 00:10:21.276
Note that it's changed
slightly in Ice Cream

00:10:21.276 --> 00:10:24.980
Sandwich, and you can see both
of the options on screen here.

00:10:24.980 --> 00:10:26.550
Then note that this doesn't
specifically

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:27.700
launch Google Music.

00:10:27.700 --> 00:10:29.140
