specify a

00:10:29.140 --> 00:10:30.790
particular music player.

00:10:30.790 --> 00:10:32.860
Any app that's capable of
playing, browsing, or

00:10:32.860 --> 00:10:35.810
manipulating music files stored
on the device can

00:10:35.810 --> 00:10:38.830
specify the category app music
in its manifest and be

00:10:38.830 --> 00:10:41.990
presented as an option when
this intent is fired.

00:10:41.990 --> 00:10:44.090
So if you're building a music
player, that's something you

00:10:44.090 --> 00:10:48.190
may want to consider when
building your app.

