run it is a real turn off.

00:28:05.500 --> 00:28:08.000
Every time I have to click the
button again, I'm that much

00:28:08.000 --> 00:28:10.955
more tempted to just hit Back,
go to the Play Store, and

00:28:10.955 --> 00:28:12.740
download something faster.

00:28:12.740 --> 00:28:14.590
You want to update your
UI a little bit.

00:28:14.590 --> 00:28:16.810
There's some iPhone-y looking
buttons, which just kind of

00:28:16.810 --> 00:28:18.650
look out of place on Android.

00:28:18.650 --> 00:28:19.470
And same--

00:28:19.470 --> 00:28:20.170
Exit button--

00:28:20.170 --> 00:28:21.750
same as Endomondo.

00:28:21.750 --> 00:28:23.820
Please get rid of
the Exit button.

00:28:23.820 --> 00:28:26.800
The setting screen in the
overall UI isn't as intuitive

00:28:26.800 --> 00:28:27.460
as it could be.

00:28:27.460 --> 00:28:28.430
I mean, it's a great app.

00:28:28.430 --> 00:28:30.690
It has a lot of the features
that I really want to see.

00:28:30.690 --> 00:28:33.020
It just feels like I have to do
a little bit too much work

00:28:33.020 --> 00:28:34.780
to be able to use it.

00:28:34.780 --> 00:28:36.580
Build with tablet mode
would be fantastic.

00:28:36.580 --> 00:28:40.600
Again, don't lock me into
portrait if you don't have to.

00:28:40.600 --> 00:28:42.510
And yeah, maybe see if you can
do something about the logo.

00:28:42.510 --> 00:28:44.480
I think you're like 90%
of the way there

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:45.780
with something awesome.

00:28:45.780 --> 00:28:47.940
You could just get rid of the
rounded corners, and suddenly,

00:28:47.940 --> 00:28:50.520
you've got something which would
be a really distinctive

00:28:50.520 --> 00:28:52.990
and really great Android logo.

00:28:52.990 --> 00:28:54.630
And finally, RunKeeper.

00:28:54.630 --> 00:28:57.865
So here, it's great to see that
you guys are doing a UI

00:28:57.865 --> 00:28:59.560
overhaul to bring in
some of those new

00:28:59.560 --> 00:29:01.130
patents like Action Bar.

00:29:01.130 --> 00:29:03.630
I definitely think it's an
opportunity for you to maybe

00:29:03.630 --> 00:29:06.000
