00:30:42.080 --> 00:30:46.990
The first one is "What's the
best way to integrate social

00:30:46.990 --> 00:30:51.350
aspects into these types of
apps?" Go ahead, and I'll ask

00:30:51.350 --> 00:30:52.070
the second one later.

00:30:52.070 --> 00:30:52.660
RETO MEIER: Sure.

00:30:52.660 --> 00:30:54.720
That's actually a good question
and something which I

00:30:54.720 --> 00:30:55.370
didn't touch on.

00:30:55.370 --> 00:30:59.300
But at least two of the apps,
Endomondo and runstastic, both

00:30:59.300 --> 00:31:03.120
have deep integration with
social features.

00:31:03.120 --> 00:31:04.280
Now, they've done it
a pretty good way.

00:31:04.280 --> 00:31:06.000
And you can see that a lot of
people will share their

00:31:06.000 --> 00:31:09.580
workouts via things like
Facebook and Twitter.

00:31:09.580 --> 00:31:15.000
And likewise, Endomondo has the
ability to actually cheer

00:31:15.000 --> 00:31:16.700
your friends on or compete
against them.

00:31:16.700 --> 00:31:20.950
I think these are all really
rich uses of social circles.

00:31:20.950 --> 00:31:23.520
It's been proven, in fact, that
with things like anything

00:31:23.520 --> 00:31:26.410
goal setting, particularly
things like exercise, having

00:31:26.410 --> 00:31:29.310
people hold you accountable is
a really great way of being

00:31:29.310 --> 00:31:33.230
able to help motivate you and
keep your willpower up.

00:31:33.230 --> 00:31:35.790
So I think the key to social
integration here on a

00:31:35.790 --> 00:31:40.270
philosophical level is to
find ways to help you be

00:31:40.270 --> 00:31:43.250
accountable to your friends
and create something

00:31:43.250 --> 00:31:46.110
competitive with people, which
is always a real help when it

00:31:46.110 --> 00:31:47.850
comes to things fitness.

00:31:47.850 --> 00:31:51.030
In terms of practical
implementation details, I

00:31:51.030 --> 00:31:54.840
think the key is really to try
and make it as smooth a path

00:31:54.840 --> 00:31:55.490
as possible.

00:31:55.490 --> 00:31:58.470
So whatever social network
you're choosing to integrate

00:31:58.470 --> 00:32:01.020
with, you want to make sure that
that sign-in flow is as

00:32:01.020 --> 00:32:01.950
smooth as possible.

00:32:01.950 --> 00:32:04.240
Like I said, I actually had
some trouble creating an

00:32:04.240 --> 00:32:06.790
account on Endomondo, and I want
this to be as much of a

00:32:06.790 --> 00:32:08.400
one-click process as possible.

00:32:08.400 --> 00:32:11.560
So whether that's signing into
Facebook, Twitter, G+, or

00:32:11.560 --> 00:32:13.680
anything else which provides
you with some of the

00:32:13.680 --> 00:32:17.680
functionality you need, you
really want to try and make

00:32:17.680 --> 00:32:19.450
that process as smooth
as possible.

00:32:19.450 --> 00:32:21.950
And ideally, make sure
it doesn't block.

00:32:21.950 --> 00:32:24.020
So I want to be able to use
the app with no social

00:32:24.020 --> 00:32:28.370
features and with no account,
and then see the reasons why

00:32:28.370 --> 00:32:31.710
hooking this into my social
network would be beneficial.

00:32:31.710 --> 00:32:33.220
And then once you've done that,
you want to make sure as

00:32:33.220 --> 00:32:34.950
well you're not doing
anything obnoxious.

00:32:34.950 --> 00:32:38.040
Make sure that you always give
the users an option as to

00:32:38.040 --> 00:32:40.320
whether they want to share
something on their social

00:32:40.320 --> 00:32:41.790
network or not.

00:32:41.790 --> 00:32:45.880
And in fact, one of the apps,
I believe it was runtastic,

00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:48.540
has a share icon, but it doesn't
actually let you share

00:32:48.540 --> 00:32:50.080
anything unless you're
logged in.

00:32:50.080 --> 00:32:51.840
And that's something you
want to avoid as well.

00:32:51.840 --> 00:32:55.300
It's great to have the social
features built in directly to

00:32:55.300 --> 00:32:58.720
those websites, if you can, just
to lower the friction.

00:32:58.720 --> 00:33:01.860
But even if I haven't chosen
to sign in with Facebook, I

00:33:01.860 --> 00:33:04.150
still want to be able to share
it using any of the apps that

00:33:04.150 --> 00:33:06.350
I have installed, which may
include things like Facebook,

00:33:06.350 --> 00:33:08.060
Twitter, or G+.

00:33:08.060 --> 00:33:10.910
So you want to make sure that
you don't limit yourself just

00:33:10.910 --> 00:33:13.210
to those tight integrations
and make sure that just

00:33:13.210 --> 00:33:16.930
standard sharing across regular
Android intent-based

00:33:16.930 --> 00:33:19.540
sharing works as well.

